07:09.680 --> 07:11.640
I would literally
eat anything right now.

07:11.723 --> 07:12.683
I mean it.

07:12.766 --> 07:13.976
Look at us.

07:14.059 --> 07:16.186
Hey, that's a family tradition.

07:16.270 --> 07:17.646
White husbands.

07:17.729 --> 07:19.815
Am I a fetish?

07:19.898 --> 07:21.483
- Don't you feel like
we're dropping the ball

07:21.567 --> 07:23.819
- on our heritage?
- Your name is Astrid

07:23.902 --> 07:25.487
from Scandinavia.

07:25.571 --> 07:27.990
I'm named after
Tony Orlando's backup singers.

07:28.073 --> 07:29.700
We're not the ones
who dropped the ball.

07:29.783 --> 07:32.160
- Well, you know what?
I--I'm picking the ball back up.

07:32.244 --> 07:34.955
I'm going to teach Viv
how to make chana bhaturas

07:35.038 --> 07:38.125
and other important things.

07:38.208 --> 07:39.459
Hey, Felix.

07:39.543 --> 07:42.045
When is your baseball
game tomorrow?

07:42.129 --> 07:44.131
Baseball's boring.

07:44.214 --> 07:45.591
- No. Wait, wait.
What do you mean?

07:45.674 --> 07:47.301
We're, we're having
such a great time together,

07:47.384 --> 07:49.303
and you're so good at it.
He's amazing.

07:50.804 --> 07:53.682
- Fine.
Let's go to stupid baseball.

07:56.018 --> 07:57.519
It's tomorrow, pal.

07:58.687 --> 08:00.272
Stupid baseball is tomorrow.

