I can tell you the ingredients
and how to cook it.

08:45.317 --> 08:46.568
- That's literally
what a recipe is.

08:46.652 --> 08:48.320
- Yeah. But no, no,
it won't be right.

08:48.403 --> 08:50.405
I don't know measurements,
you taste as you go.

08:51.532 --> 08:52.824
Why don't you
come over with the kids?

08:52.908 --> 08:54.284
We'll spend the day
together cooking and,

08:54.368 --> 08:55.994
and Corey can turn it
into one of his videos.

08:56.078 --> 08:57.246
No, God. No, no, no.

08:57.329 --> 08:58.705
I didn't want it
to be this big thing.

08:58.789 --> 09:02.042
I just want it to be this--
this very special intimate,

09:02.125 --> 09:04.211
passing down
family wisdom moment

09:04.294 --> 09:07.297
that Viv can look back
on years from now and think,

09:07.381 --> 09:09.508
"God, she was a good mom.
