Fans wanna know.
Baseball.

09:56.054 --> 09:58.599
Do you hate it,
and is it your dad's fault?

09:58.682 --> 10:01.685
- I don't hate baseball.
- Yes, it's fun, right?

10:01.768 --> 10:03.353
I guess. It's just...

